Paper: hep-th/9609235

Date: 1996-09-30

Title: Nonadiabatic Geometric Phase in Quaternionic Hilbert Space

Authors: Stephen L. Adler and Jeeva Anandan

Comments: 14 pages, plain Tex, no figures

Journal-ref: Found.Phys. 26 (1996) 1579-1589

We develop the theory of the nonadiabatic geometric phase, in both theAbelian and non-Abelian cases, in quaternionic Hilbert space.